OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day with
OL,6,Fvariable amounts of cloud, perhaps a
OL,7,Fcloudy start to the day. Some bright
OL,8,For sunny spells developing at times.
OL,9,FLight winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fa little late brightness. Then the
OL,13,Frest of the night will remain dry with
OL,14,Fvariable amounts of cloud and clear
OL,15,Fperiods.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FA dry day with some low
OL,18,Fcloud around but the chance of some
OL,19,Fbrightness at times too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
